{"tid":1441664,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人知點解黑警咁鍾意搵sp/非禮/強姦啲女仔？","createTime":"2019-08-10T17:07:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T01:16:08.000Z","uid":105590,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"873ef5ed539cd0f3fe1e260058e52d6d08447581","tid":1441664,"uid":105590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:07:42.000Z","msg":"例如<br />\n<br />\n之前查身分證攞電話再返屋企溝女啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n旺角警處強姦案啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n天水圍男警除女仔底褲望 再帶佢返警處生死未卜啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n又例如沙蛇約sp返警處抱屌啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次非禮騎空姐 再迫佢返警處唔知做啲咩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋重有超多 不能盡錄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n真係由細聽呢啲聽到大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解咁冇道德既一班爛仔同咸濕佬會做到維持治安既警察？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n真係對警察冇哂希望 以後都唔會信佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1843197b51e2cd1c8351e7cb5b64ed757a7bf994","tid":1441664,"uid":105590,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:09:50.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"4bef62fb3f13d556eecfe6b30520560896c29c99","tid":1441664,"uid":105590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:19:49.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"73c3205e67c7bf03310bf4933376df